<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/143120-how-do-us-homeowners-feel-about-paying">How do US homeowners feel about paying about 2% in annual property taxes on the value a house they may actually owe money on, while someone who owns millions in securities pays no property tax on it, and even passes it on to heirs tax free? I realize mortgage interest and property tax is tax deductible, but the deductions never came close to covering my property taxes.</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_143120'><a id="like_count_community_question_143120" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/143120?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">8 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F18736925-capital-in-the-twenty-first-century">like</a></span>

</li>
