</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/7264087-scott">Scott</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Rich Williams is incorrect. Piketty proposes the wealth tax <b>instead</b> of the property tax (although in addition to other taxes), because real estate pro<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Rich Williams is incorrect. Piketty proposes the wealth tax <b>instead</b> of the property tax (although in addition to other taxes), because real estate property would be included within the wealth tax. <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
